<P>
ATHLETES OF THE WEEK; DAN STYLES; LAGUNA BEACH, JR.; VOLLEYBALL / OUTSIDE 
HITTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Styles, who has the highest amateur beach volleyball rating, is honing his 
indoor game, and Laguna Beach Coach Michael Soylular says he is one of the best 
swing hitters around. Last week, Styles made believers out of Laguna Hills, 
Trabuco Hills and Dana Hills. Friday night against Dana Hills, then the 
top-ranked team in the county, Styles had 21 kills in a four-game victory.He 
had 14 kills in a three-game sweep of Trabuco Hills and a sweep of Laguna 
Hills. The Artists (5-0), who were ranked third in the county last week, are 
now No. 2. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
