1-0 victory over Kennedy. 
</P>
<P>
 * Joe Reynoza, El Modena, had 45 kills in a five-game volleyball victory over 
Valencia. 
</P>
<P>
 * Jeff Ritter, Brea-Olinda, won the 50 freestyle in 23.27 seconds and the 100 
free in 50.71 at the Sonora Invitational. He's also undefeated in dual meets. 
