<DATE>
<P>
March 29, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1327 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FEBRUARY RESTAURANT CLOSURES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The county Department of Health Services has the power to shut down food 
facilities for as long as necessary for the owners to correct conditions that 
pose a danger to the public health. Here is a list of the restaurants closed 
during February. 
