 Another auto nameplate is joining Volvo, BMW and other foreign cars already 
being imported through the Port of Hueneme.The new make, Britain's Land Rover 
Discovery, is due to roll off Wallenius Lines' Madame Butterfly shortly before 
noon today. 
</P>
<P>
 Discovery, described as an upscale four-wheel-drive vehicle, will more than 
double the number of Land Rover units entering the U. S. market through Port 
