<P>
SAVANT, DRAKE SET FOR 'ACTING GAY' DISCUSSION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Actors Doug Savant ("Melrose Place") and David Drake ("The Night Larry Kramer 
Kissed Me") will be featured on an April 16 panel discussion on the topic of 
"Acting Gay." 
</P>
<P>
 The free panel, which begins at 2 p.m. at Pomona College's Lyman Hall, is part 
of the college's speaker series "The Hollywood Connection." 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (909) 621-8018. 
</P>
