<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Semtech Corp. earnings -- In a March 22 story, The Times overstated the 
Newbury Park electronics manufacturer's annual profit. In its fiscal year that 
ended Jan. 30, Semtech actually earned $95,000, down 78% from its $431,000 net 
income in the previous year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
