</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Turkish elections -- Part of the headline on a report Monday about results 
from local elections in Turkey incorrectly characterized the prime minister's 
position in the political spectrum. The political party headed by Prime 
Minister Tansu Ciller, the True Path Party, is conservative. 
</P>
